      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail reflects a level of preservation synonymous with investment-grade quality. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle in its absolute prime. Inspections are welcomed to verify its unrivaled state.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
